local Parallel = require "actions/Parallel" local Do = require "actions/Do" local Wait = require "actions/Wait"
return function(self, dt) if not self.scene:playerMovable() or self.stopMoving then return end
local fx = self.scene.player.fx if self.scene.player.noGas or self.nofollow then fx = 25 end
if self.bx < -1 then self.bx = self.bx + 1 elseif self.bx > 1 then self.bx = self.bx - 1 else self.bx = 0 end
local pbx = self.scene.player.bx if pbx > 0 then pbx = pbx + 1 end self.x = self.x + (fx + self.bx + pbx) * (dt/0.016)
if self.y + self.sprite.h > self.scene.player.y - 56 then self.y = self.y - 2*(dt/0.016) elseif self.y + self.sprite.h < self.scene.player.y - 64 then self.y = self.y + 2*(dt/0.016) end end

local BasicNPC = require "object/BasicNPC" local Do = require "actions/Do" local Animate = require "actions/Animate"
return function(self, player) if self.hit then return end self.hit = true local npc = BasicNPC( player.scene, {name = "objects"}, {name = "mecharm", x = player.x + 200, y = 180, width = 300, height = 92, properties = {nocollision = true, sprite = "art/sprites/mechaarmrace.png"}} ) player.scene:addObject(npc) npc:run { Animate(npc.sprite, "down"), Do(function() print("got em!") end) } end
